Package org.influxdata.platform

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    AuthorizationClient
    The client of the InfluxData Platform that implement Authorization HTTP API endpoint.
    BucketClient
    The client of the InfluxData Platform that implement Bucket HTTP API endpoint.
    OrganizationClient
    The client of the InfluxData Platform that implement Organization HTTP API endpoint.
    PlatformClient
    The client of the InfluxData Platform for Time Series that implements HTTP API defined by Influx API Service swagger.yml.
    PlatformClientReactive
    The reference RxJava client for the Influx 2.0 OSS Platform that allows query and write in a reactive way.
    QueryClient
    The client of the InfluxData Platform that implement Query HTTP API endpoint.
    QueryClientReactive
    The client that allow perform Flux query against the InfluxData Platform by a reactive way.
    ScraperClient
    Represents an HTTP API handler for scraper targets.
    SourceClient
    The client of the InfluxData Platform that implement Source HTTP API endpoint.
    TaskClient
    The client of the InfluxData Platform that implement Task HTTP API endpoint.
    UserClient
    The client of the InfluxData Platform that implement User HTTP API endpoint.
    WriteClient
    Write time-series data into InfluxData Platform 2.0.
    WriteClientReactive
    Write time-series data into InfluxData Platform 2.0.

    PlatformClientFactory
    The Factory that create a instance of a Platform client.
    PlatformClientReactiveFactory
    The Factory that create a instance of a Platform reactive client.
